-- China Bond, Forex Markets' Size `Too Small,' CBRC's Zhang Guangping Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-16T03:22:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-16/china-bond-forex-markets-size-too-small-cbrc-s-zhang-guangping-says.html
The size of China’s bond and foreign
exchange markets is still “too small” compared with global
markets, Zhang Guangping, deputy chief of the Shanghai bureau of
the China Banking Regulatory Commission, said at a financial
forum in Shanghai.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
